					</div>
					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Peter Mishler</h4>
												<p>Peter Mishler is the author of two collections of poetry, <em>Fludde</em> (winner of Sarabande Books' Kathryn A. Morton Prize) and <em>Children in Tactical Gear</em> (winner of the Iowa Poetry Prize, forthcoming from the University of Iowa Press in Spring 2024). His newest poems appear in <em>The Paris Review, American Poetry Review, Poetry London, The Iowa Review,</em> and <em>Granta. </em> He is also the author of a book of meditative reflections for public school educators from Andrews McMeel Publishing.</p>
					</div>
